{"type":"message","id":"f6473c3b","parentId":"fc21933a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:14:03.582Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session in the last 5 minutes is the current cron session itself (agent=main:cron:3709e1d2...). This is the session that just started from the cron job. There are no other active user conversations.\n\nHowever, I need to be careful here. The session that just ran was the cron session itself. It hasn't received a user message recently. The question is whether there are any other user sessions that are active.\n\nLooking at the session - it's the cron session running, and it has only sent system messages and tool calls. There's no actual user message in this session.\n\nBut wait - the question says \"如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息）\". This session is a cron-triggered session, not a user conversation. I should check if there are any actual user conversations active.\n\n\nThe only session showing up is the cron job itself, which means there are no active user conversations right now. I should proceed with the autonomous learning task by searching for recent developments in enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"8948b57068630eaabca11e749e9c646ba801dd17bb3b00e2fc4c568c7c69ef2c"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前没有用户活跃对话，只有cron任务自身的session。执行自主学习任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6ektoemn42o5_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":815,"output":282,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45078,"cost":{"input":0.0002445,"output":0.0003384,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019023299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774682035288}}
{"type":"message","id":"93b0ddca","parentId":"f6473c3b","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:14:03.588Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6ektoemn42o5_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774682043585}}
